2070
00:42:32,000 --> 00:42:34,000
[SPEAKER_05] Kada niste saznali niko je ubio vaši člani?

2071
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:36,000
[SPEAKER_07] Ne znam da moće i koreć kog volio.

2072
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:38,000
[SPEAKER_07] Ali neće niko ne znaše.

2073
00:42:38,000 --> 00:42:39,000
[SPEAKER_07] Nisam vidio nikoga.

2074
00:42:39,000 --> 00:42:40,000
[SPEAKER_07] Nisam vidio nikoga.

2075
00:42:40,000 --> 00:42:42,000
[SPEAKER_07] Nisam bio nikoga kad sam tošao kući.

2076
00:42:42,000 --> 00:42:44,000
[SPEAKER_07] Ne mreš sad reći nako na pamet.

2077
00:42:44,000 --> 00:42:47,000
[SPEAKER_07] Ubiti dušu, a ne znaš.

2078
00:42:47,000 --> 00:42:49,000
[SPEAKER_02] Najme krivlije kad odajem doktoru.

2079
00:42:49,000 --> 00:42:51,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ona si ide u bako.

2080
00:42:51,000 --> 00:42:53,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ja si idim u bako.

2081
00:42:53,000 --> 00:42:54,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ona ti pričaju.

2082
00:42:54,000 --> 00:42:56,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ona dobiva za onog...

2083
00:42:56,000 --> 00:42:59,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ko joj je poginu 300 maraka.

2084
00:42:59,000 --> 00:43:01,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ona ja dobiva za o 300 maraka.

2085
00:43:01,000 --> 00:43:03,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ubilu mi mačku.

2086
00:43:03,000 --> 00:43:04,000
[SPEAKER_02] Dobivam moja.

2087
00:43:04,000 --> 00:43:07,000
[SPEAKER_02] Vrijedna je njezna mačka nego moj čača i mater.

2088
00:43:07,000 --> 00:43:09,000
[SPEAKER_02] A ja nisam dobila nikad ništa.

2089
00:43:09,000 --> 00:43:10,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ne moram dobiti.

2090
00:43:10,000 --> 00:43:12,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ja hvala Bogu živim bez toga.

2091
00:43:12,000 --> 00:43:15,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ali ako je vrijedna njezna mačka, što nije...

2092
00:43:15,000 --> 00:43:18,000
[SPEAKER_02] Zad nisu vrijedni moji roditelji.

2093
00:43:18,000 --> 00:43:20,000
[SPEAKER_02] Još vrijedni.

2094
00:43:20,000 --> 00:43:23,000
[SPEAKER_02] Viš će jedne mačke uspoređu.

2095
00:43:23,000 --> 00:43:26,000
[SPEAKER_02] Život i jedne osobe i dvija.

2096
00:43:26,000 --> 00:43:29,000
[SPEAKER_05] Kako čovjek zapravo da ne ostane umržnji?

2097
00:43:29,000 --> 00:43:31,000
[SPEAKER_05] Što je vama pomoglo da ipak...

2098
00:43:31,000 --> 00:43:33,000
[SPEAKER_07] Šta ja znam...

2099
00:43:33,000 --> 00:43:36,000
[SPEAKER_05] Da ipak da vas ta mržnja ne zarobi kasti?

2100
00:43:36,000 --> 00:43:38,000
[SPEAKER_05] Evo, ubijeni su vam roditelji...

2101
00:43:38,000 --> 00:43:39,000
[SPEAKER_05] A mržnja je bolesti.

2102
00:43:39,000 --> 00:43:42,000
[SPEAKER_07] Da čovjek oboli i teško je to.

2103
00:43:42,000 --> 00:43:44,000
[SPEAKER_07] I vjerati.

2104
00:43:44,000 --> 00:43:46,000
[SPEAKER_07] Ne dozvoljava da ga mrziš.

2105
00:43:46,000 --> 00:43:47,000
[SPEAKER_07] A ne mreš li zaboravit tako.

2106
00:43:47,000 --> 00:43:49,000
[SPEAKER_07] Zaboravit ne mreš nikad.

2107
00:43:49,000 --> 00:43:50,000
[SPEAKER_07] Te bi se to vaze i umjeđeš.

2108
00:43:50,000 --> 00:43:51,000
[SPEAKER_07] Mi će to...

2109
00:43:51,000 --> 00:43:54,000
[SPEAKER_07] Te bi pred očima i sve vidi i znaš.

2110
00:43:54,000 --> 00:43:55,000
[SPEAKER_07] Te upornoći te zne.

2111
00:43:55,000 --> 00:43:57,000
[SPEAKER_07] Sve vidiš i sve znaš.

2112
00:43:57,000 --> 00:44:02,000
[SPEAKER_04] A ja oprašćam zato što sam katolkinja i što sam mrladica.

2113
00:44:02,000 --> 00:44:04,000
[SPEAKER_04] I molim se dragom Bogu.

2114
00:44:04,000 --> 00:44:05,000
[SPEAKER_04] I...

2115
00:44:05,000 --> 00:44:07,000
[SPEAKER_04] Zaboravit ne mogu nikad.

2116
00:44:07,000 --> 00:44:12,000
[SPEAKER_04] Ja još nikad nisam zaspala da to nije prozglavo prošlo.

2117
00:44:12,000 --> 00:44:15,000
[SPEAKER_04] A da nije tableta...

2118
00:44:15,000 --> 00:44:18,000
[SPEAKER_04] Ja pa deset tableta da nas popijem.

2119
00:44:18,000 --> 00:44:19,000
[SPEAKER_04] Meni neka doje.

2120
00:44:19,000 --> 00:44:22,000
[SPEAKER_04] Ja sam depresija da bi se po lupala pokođa.

2121
00:44:22,000 --> 00:44:26,000
[SPEAKER_04] Ali boh, milostini, klunica i zabiti to me drža.

2122
00:44:26,000 --> 00:44:30,000
[SPEAKER_05] Ste uspjeli oprostiti?

2123
00:44:30,000 --> 00:44:32,000
[SPEAKER_03] Pa ja šta ću? Šta ću im drugo?

2124
00:44:32,000 --> 00:44:33,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ne znam da znam.

2125
00:44:33,000 --> 00:44:34,000
[SPEAKER_02] Nema te mržnje premaj.

2126
00:44:34,000 --> 00:44:35,000
[SPEAKER_05] Ma ne ne.

2127
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:36,000
[SPEAKER_02] Taka je naša vjera.

2128
00:44:36,000 --> 00:44:39,000
[SPEAKER_02] Oprosti svakome.

2129
00:44:39,000 --> 00:44:42,000
[SPEAKER_02] Molim za neprijatelje kao i za prijatelje.

2130
00:44:42,000 --> 00:44:45,000
[SPEAKER_02] I ja njima opraštam.

2131
00:44:45,000 --> 00:44:47,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ima Boga Gondje Sucu i ja.

2132
00:44:47,000 --> 00:44:49,000
[SPEAKER_05] Jeste uspjeli oprostiti?

2133
00:44:49,000 --> 00:44:51,000
[SPEAKER_06] Ono šta je.

2134
00:44:51,000 --> 00:44:52,000
[SPEAKER_06] Oprosti?

2135
00:44:52,000 --> 00:44:53,000
[SPEAKER_06] Može.

2136
00:44:53,000 --> 00:44:55,000
[SPEAKER_06] A zabraviti nikada.

2137
00:44:55,000 --> 00:44:59,000
[SPEAKER_06] Oprosti mora zabraviti.

2138
00:44:59,000 --> 00:45:02,000
[SPEAKER_05] Koko mi opraštanje pomoglo?

2139
00:45:02,000 --> 00:45:04,000
[SPEAKER_05] Rekli ste depresija i...

2140
00:45:04,000 --> 00:45:06,000
[SPEAKER_05] Ojoj, ojoj.

2141
00:45:06,000 --> 00:45:07,000
[SPEAKER_05] Mnogo posljedica.

2142
00:45:07,000 --> 00:45:10,000
[SPEAKER_04] Pet godina sam sam ali ičila u Zagrebu. Pet godina.

2143
00:45:10,000 --> 00:45:14,000
[SPEAKER_05] Slažite se samo da praštanje nema alternativu.

2144
00:45:14,000 --> 00:45:15,000
[SPEAKER_05] Da je najvažnije oprostiti.

2145
00:45:15,000 --> 00:45:17,000
[SPEAKER_04] Najvažnije oprostiti.

2146
00:45:17,000 --> 00:45:19,000
[SPEAKER_05] To mi je pomoglo.

2147
00:45:19,000 --> 00:45:21,000
[SPEAKER_05] Jeste uspjeli odmah oprostiti?

2148
00:45:21,000 --> 00:45:22,000
[SPEAKER_05] Al vi ste svečenik.

2149
00:45:22,000 --> 00:45:23,000
[SPEAKER_05] Znamo da je nauk takav.

2150
00:45:23,000 --> 00:45:25,000
[SPEAKER_05] Međutim, roditelji...

2151
00:45:27,000 --> 00:45:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jeste me boli.

2152
00:45:29,000 --> 00:45:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prežaliti je bilo jako teško sestru i roditelje, pa čak i ove druge koje sam poznavao.

2153
00:45:35,000 --> 00:45:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mene je misijski rad jako puno pomogao.

2154
00:45:37,000 --> 00:45:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam ne bi zadržavao u misiji, nego kad bi se probudio i za doručka i viša u sela.

2155
00:45:42,000 --> 00:45:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Cijeli dan sa ljudima u selu.

2156
00:45:44,000 --> 00:45:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ili evangelizirajući, ili poučavajući vjeronavuk.

2157
00:45:46,000 --> 00:45:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ili mi osalizjanci volimo toratori, igrati sa s djecom i tako.

2158
00:45:50,000 --> 00:45:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da sam od jutra pa do večera uvijek u selu, da ne razmišljam o tome.

2159
00:45:55,000 --> 00:46:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer onda te vuče ta nostalgija, onda dođe kakvih tih misli.

2160
00:46:00,000 --> 00:46:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] I meni je to pomoglo da ja nadiđem tu situaciju.

2161
00:46:03,000 --> 00:46:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Što se tiče oprost, ja sam imao prostio.

2162
00:46:05,000 --> 00:46:08,000
[SPEAKER_04] Bili smo s njima dobri i kumovali se.

2163
00:46:08,000 --> 00:46:10,000
[SPEAKER_04] Išla dica zajedno u školu.

2164
00:46:10,000 --> 00:46:12,000
[SPEAKER_04] Samo s temanima.

2165
00:46:12,000 --> 00:46:14,000
[SPEAKER_05] Jesu to ljudi s kojima ste se nekad družili?

2166
00:46:14,000 --> 00:46:17,000
[SPEAKER_07] No vidjeli išli i bacali kamera, bacali kamera.

2167
00:46:17,000 --> 00:46:19,000
[SPEAKER_07] Igrali mnogo medisir.

2168
00:46:19,000 --> 00:46:20,000
[SPEAKER_07] Bio meo jadan.

2169
00:46:20,000 --> 00:46:22,000
[SPEAKER_07] Jero Mevara.

2170
00:46:22,000 --> 00:46:24,000
[SPEAKER_07] Oni je pogilo me ovdje ko škole.

2171
00:46:24,000 --> 00:46:27,000
[SPEAKER_07] Ono da pogilo im Hođa jadan.

2172
00:46:27,000 --> 00:46:28,000
[SPEAKER_07] Mi mislimo Aram jadan.

2173
00:46:28,000 --> 00:46:30,000
[SPEAKER_07] Biložač u školi.

2174
00:46:30,000 --> 00:46:32,000
[SPEAKER_07] Kad nije bio u Aram, ko bio bio u Hođa.

2175
00:46:32,000 --> 00:46:34,000
[SPEAKER_07] Hođa bio.

2176
00:46:34,000 --> 00:46:36,000
[SPEAKER_07] A isti imo u Aram jadan.

2177
00:46:36,000 --> 00:46:38,000
[SPEAKER_07] Mislimo s tog postao je Biložač u školi.

2178
00:46:38,000 --> 00:46:40,000
[SPEAKER_07] S naki dan skupaj bili prijatelji.

2179
00:46:40,000 --> 00:46:42,000
[SPEAKER_07] I bili ste prijatelji?

2180
00:46:42,000 --> 00:46:44,000
[SPEAKER_05] I bili ste prijatelji.

2181
00:46:44,000 --> 00:46:46,000
[SPEAKER_07] Prijatelji bili čolo prijatelji.

2182
00:46:46,000 --> 00:46:47,000
[SPEAKER_07] Ja sam mislimo poginu Mođare.

2183
00:46:47,000 --> 00:46:48,000
[SPEAKER_07] Vidio sam posle Mođareva.

2184
00:46:48,000 --> 00:46:49,000
[SPEAKER_07] Živ je bio.

2185
00:46:49,000 --> 00:46:50,000
[SPEAKER_07] Živ je.

2186
00:46:50,000 --> 00:46:51,000
[SPEAKER_07] I sad je živ.

2187
00:46:51,000 --> 00:46:52,000
[SPEAKER_06] Još je živ.

2188
00:46:52,000 --> 00:46:54,000
[SPEAKER_06] Susičio je s ovo muslimanima i s svima.

2189
00:46:54,000 --> 00:46:58,000
[SPEAKER_06] Oni samo naređen podig njegov.

2190
00:46:58,000 --> 00:46:59,000
[SPEAKER_06] Dravo, zdravo.

2191
00:46:59,000 --> 00:47:01,000
[SPEAKER_06] A nea komunikacija neke i toga.

2192
00:47:01,000 --> 00:47:03,000
[SPEAKER_07] Sad sam mi se svetamo sa tim muslimanima.

2193
00:47:03,000 --> 00:47:05,000
[SPEAKER_07] I oni nisu ni.

2194
00:47:05,000 --> 00:47:06,000
[SPEAKER_07] Oni svi krivi.

2195
00:47:06,000 --> 00:47:08,000
[SPEAKER_07] Znaš, ima uđi pošteni muslimana.

2196
00:47:08,000 --> 00:47:09,000
[SPEAKER_07] Pravi uđi.

2197
00:47:09,000 --> 00:47:11,000
[SPEAKER_07] Koji žale isto uviču.

2198
00:47:11,000 --> 00:47:13,000
[SPEAKER_07] Čeo sam poginut jac, poginut jac, poginut jac.

2199
00:47:13,000 --> 00:47:14,000
[SPEAKER_07] Čerka, djete.

2200
00:47:14,000 --> 00:47:15,000
[SPEAKER_07] Pa, šta su radili?

2201
00:47:15,000 --> 00:47:16,000
[SPEAKER_07] Pa.

2202
00:47:16,000 --> 00:47:17,000
[SPEAKER_07] A u radili, radili.

2203
00:47:17,000 --> 00:47:18,000
[SPEAKER_07] Nisu radili ti, a šta.

2204
00:47:18,000 --> 00:47:20,000
[SPEAKER_07] U radili su tvoji.

2205
00:47:20,000 --> 00:47:22,000
[SPEAKER_07] U radili su moji radi na drugom mjestu.

2206
00:47:22,000 --> 00:47:23,000
[SPEAKER_07] Ja znam.

2207
00:47:23,000 --> 00:47:25,000
[SPEAKER_07] Ali uglavnom, vidimo se.

2208
00:47:25,000 --> 00:47:26,000
[SPEAKER_07] Ja sam radio.

2209
00:47:26,000 --> 00:47:28,000
[SPEAKER_07] I oni loze meni po papire.

2210
00:47:28,000 --> 00:47:30,000
[SPEAKER_07] Rodni Lis, pat, pšiva djete.

2211
00:47:30,000 --> 00:47:31,000
[SPEAKER_07] Moran su.

2212
00:47:31,000 --> 00:47:32,000
[SPEAKER_07] Poslu.

2213
00:47:32,000 --> 00:47:34,000
[SPEAKER_07] Še mača školen tu bila.

2214
00:47:34,000 --> 00:47:36,000
[SPEAKER_07] Mači mužda sve ne tu.

2215
00:47:36,000 --> 00:47:37,000
[SPEAKER_05] S njima imate korektne odnose?

2216
00:47:37,000 --> 00:47:38,000
[SPEAKER_07] Pa morao se ima.

2217
00:47:38,000 --> 00:47:39,000
[SPEAKER_07] Moran doći.

2218
00:47:39,000 --> 00:47:41,000
[SPEAKER_07] Možemo da živi iz Nemačke i Zavske.

2219
00:47:41,000 --> 00:47:43,000
[SPEAKER_07] iz Švičarske dobije penziju.

2220
00:47:43,000 --> 00:47:44,000
[SPEAKER_07] Moran doći na dom.

2221
00:47:44,000 --> 00:47:45,000
[SPEAKER_07] Potrebi da živim.

2222
00:47:45,000 --> 00:47:46,000
[SPEAKER_07] Da obvjerim.

2223
00:47:46,000 --> 00:47:48,000
[SPEAKER_07] Kako ži nećemo penziju da to.

2224
00:47:48,000 --> 00:47:49,000
[SPEAKER_05] Ne obi.

2225
00:47:49,000 --> 00:47:51,000
[SPEAKER_05] Je vam teško bilo doći ponovo uzdol?

2226
00:47:51,000 --> 00:47:55,000
[SPEAKER_05] Uzdol se promijenio od ono na kako je bio u vašem djetinstvu.

2227
00:47:55,000 --> 00:47:57,000
[SPEAKER_05] Kako vidite budućnost sada ovdje?

2228
00:47:57,000 --> 00:48:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, evo, čovjek bi čak očekivao da neće biti nikakvog života na uzdolu

2229
00:48:03,000 --> 00:48:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] nakon toga što se dogodilo.

2230
00:48:05,000 --> 00:48:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam ja došao, moj brat im ima u gore kuću, novu.

2231
00:48:10,000 --> 00:48:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve smo mi to prekrižili.

2232
00:48:13,000 --> 00:48:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer kuća je bila granatirana, štale su spaljene.

2233
00:48:16,000 --> 00:48:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on je sam rekao ono koji su ostali, nek svaki uzme šta hoće.

2234
00:48:19,000 --> 00:48:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on je svaki izgubio neku nadu za neki obstanak ili život.

2235
00:48:23,000 --> 00:48:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] i stanovništvo se pokrenulo.

2236
00:48:25,000 --> 00:48:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Stanovništvo je nakon toga, ošto su nastradali, su nastradali, drugo je sve otišlo.

2237
00:48:30,000 --> 00:48:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ta naša sela koji su nastradali, nikad se nisu obnovila, u smislu da se ljudi vrate.

2238
00:48:36,000 --> 00:48:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mnoge sa kuća obnovila, ljudi su učinili neki napor da se to obnovi.

2239
00:48:41,000 --> 00:48:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali nema ljudi, selo bez ljudi, mislim nema nikakva vrijednost ni selo.

2240
00:48:47,000 --> 00:48:54,000
[SPEAKER_07] Nemačko, koji mi? Nema sve to napuša svake godine.

2241
00:48:54,000 --> 00:48:58,000
[SPEAKER_07] Onde je nas bilo 700 djaka, sad nas ima 20.

2242
00:48:58,000 --> 00:49:00,000
[SPEAKER_05] 700 djaka?

2243
00:49:00,000 --> 00:49:04,000
[SPEAKER_07] 700 djaka je bilo 75, 36, 7 i dalje.

2244
00:49:04,000 --> 00:49:07,000
[SPEAKER_07] Pa ja sam rođen 1556.

2245
00:49:07,000 --> 00:49:12,000
[SPEAKER_07] Onde je upisano matu rođeni 157 nas, što muški i jenski.

2246
00:49:12,000 --> 00:49:16,000
[SPEAKER_07] To je bilo nešto i muslimana, nas je bilo jedno 75%.

2247
00:49:16,000 --> 00:49:18,000
[SPEAKER_07] Nije možda 25%.

2248
00:49:18,000 --> 00:49:21,000
[SPEAKER_07] Sad boga godišta ima 100 osparo živi.

2249
00:49:21,000 --> 00:49:23,000
[SPEAKER_07] 56 godišta.

2250
00:49:23,000 --> 00:49:25,000
[SPEAKER_07] 100 se nas ima živi od 157.

2251
00:49:25,000 --> 00:49:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ipak 30 godina nakon svega toga ima još života tu.

2252
00:49:30,000 --> 00:49:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Izgleda je narod ipak čvršći nego što smo mi očekivali.

2253
00:49:33,000 --> 00:49:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] I valjda ta nostalgija za mjestom gdje se rođen

2254
00:49:37,000 --> 00:49:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] ili ljubav prema ovom mjestu.

2255
00:49:40,000 --> 00:49:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda smo svi svjeseni da je to natopljeno mjesto krvlju mučenika,

2256
00:49:43,000 --> 00:49:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne samo ovih zadnjih nego i prijašnjih generacija.

2257
00:49:45,000 --> 00:49:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] i mi koji smo tu rođeni nas tu buče.

2258
00:49:47,000 --> 00:49:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] I mi se uvijek vraćamo.

2259
00:49:49,000 --> 00:49:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Evo je moj brate ove godine prve dva mjesece i nevijest.

2260
00:49:52,000 --> 00:49:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad god dođem, ja tu dođem.

2261
00:49:54,000 --> 00:49:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] A moramo i zahvaliti svim svećenicima,

2262
00:49:57,000 --> 00:50:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] osobe to župniku Miljenku Čalti.

2263
00:50:00,000 --> 00:50:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja misle da bez njega ne bi bilo upustala.

2264
00:50:04,000 --> 00:50:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Misle, ne bi se obnovio, ne bi narod.

2265
00:50:06,000 --> 00:50:09,000
[SPEAKER_07] To je bio župnik Miljenku Čaltu.

2266
00:50:09,000 --> 00:50:11,000
[SPEAKER_07] On je to ufala Bog izgonu.

2267
00:50:11,000 --> 00:50:12,000
[SPEAKER_07] I ovo je sredio.

2268
00:50:12,000 --> 00:50:14,000
[SPEAKER_07] I ovu crkvi obnovio i dole to.

2269
00:50:14,000 --> 00:50:16,000
[SPEAKER_07] On je bilo njega tada,

2270
00:50:16,000 --> 00:50:18,000
[SPEAKER_07] ne bi to ništa ni napravilo.

2271
00:50:18,000 --> 00:50:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je se potrudio u tom svom svećeničkom radu

2272
00:50:22,000 --> 00:50:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] da bude, recimo tako, i menedžerište.

2273
00:50:25,000 --> 00:50:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja znam da traži sredstva za obnovu.

2274
00:50:27,000 --> 00:50:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] i to što sad nas vidite.

2275
00:50:28,000 --> 00:50:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] To moglo biti u sred grada.

2276
00:50:29,000 --> 00:50:31,000
[SPEAKER_05] Jel vjerojete u suživot?

2277
00:50:31,000 --> 00:50:35,000
[SPEAKER_05] Da može nakon svega toga biti ponovo suživot i povjerenje?

2278
00:50:35,000 --> 00:50:38,000
[SPEAKER_02] Može biti, ali nikad više ako što je bio.

2279
00:50:38,000 --> 00:50:41,000
[SPEAKER_02] Nikada.

2280
00:50:41,000 --> 00:50:43,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ja nisam nikada sa njima bila ljubitelj.

2281
00:50:43,000 --> 00:50:46,000
[SPEAKER_02] Da sam se s njima, što kažu, družila

2282
00:50:46,000 --> 00:50:49,000
[SPEAKER_02] ili pila kavo sa njima ili oča nekad.

2283
00:50:49,000 --> 00:50:51,000
[SPEAKER_02] Dobro, i nisam bila izom sučao.

2284
00:50:51,000 --> 00:50:53,000
[SPEAKER_02] Vrđićima provamo dalje su od nas.

2285
00:50:53,000 --> 00:50:56,000
[SPEAKER_05] Jel vjerojete da je u budućnosti moguć suživot ponovo

2286
00:50:56,000 --> 00:50:58,000
[SPEAKER_05] i povjerenje.

2287
00:50:58,000 --> 00:51:02,000
[SPEAKER_07] Pa i sad, vjerujem.

2288
00:51:02,000 --> 00:51:04,000
[SPEAKER_07] Vjerujem.

2289
00:51:04,000 --> 00:51:06,000
[SPEAKER_07] Ipak, narad je dobar.

2290
00:51:06,000 --> 00:51:08,000
[SPEAKER_07] Političar ne valjaju.

2291
00:51:08,000 --> 00:51:10,000
[SPEAKER_07] Političar ne valjaju.

2292
00:51:10,000 --> 00:51:12,000
[SPEAKER_07] Političar sred, radi narad je dobar.

2293
00:51:12,000 --> 00:51:14,000
[SPEAKER_07] Narad pač, narad je srotija.

2294
00:51:14,000 --> 00:51:16,000
[SPEAKER_07] I nije ovaj naš.

2295
00:51:16,000 --> 00:51:18,000
[SPEAKER_07] Međutim, oni sam neki obogatnih stisima, ništa.

2296
00:51:18,000 --> 00:51:20,000
[SPEAKER_07] Sad su oni bogataži, miljoneri.

2297
00:51:20,000 --> 00:51:22,000
[SPEAKER_07] I oni drmaju, hradaju.

2298
00:51:22,000 --> 00:51:24,000
[SPEAKER_07] U nas koši iša.

2299
00:51:24,000 --> 00:51:26,000
[SPEAKER_07] i jedno i drugi.

2300
00:51:26,000 --> 00:51:28,000
[SPEAKER_07] I jeli za žaleko i mi.

2301
00:51:28,000 --> 00:51:30,000
[SPEAKER_05] Evo, dobili ste i unuke.

